      <body>4443ed2 proposal: InterfaceConnectionInstance - assumptions BErealization and contracts Core dependency (selects): InterfaceConnection: - AssumedItemSelect (not OK) --- it is assumed that there will be backward contamination even though these two things are connected. - AssumptionAssignmentSelect (not OK) -- example TBD - ContractAssignmentSelect (not OK) -- OEM agrees to share the use of the (fibre optic cable) connection with supplier allowing them to do some analysis - BreakdownElementRealizationSelect (not OK) --- when connect headphones to mobile phone it can be a realization of a music player </body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586175604299_843716_75060" xmi:uuid="1c469f9f-eb7e-4884-8271-be0290280e5d" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585827886878_58822_81283"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509527911695_917748_38014"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: BreakdownElementStructuralAssociation: - AssumptionContextItem Core dependency (selects): BreakdownElementViewRelationship: - AssumptionAssignmentSelect (not OK) ---e.g. assume the component is not going to overheat because a "provide cooling" function as been assigned</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586259276860_627041_70455" xmi:uuid="1f7d7c7b-bb73-48d0-a235-e1577c41db8a" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1548953037133_239952_84727"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1584351663754_402995_65909"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1584355870537_59596_69901"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: Method (TaskMethod : ActivityMethod) - AssumptionAssignmentSelect (not OK) -- "there is a method therefore I assume I will be able to do this activity" (assumption on the ActualActivity with the context of the ActivityMethod)</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585214542532_440495_65578" xmi:uuid="23c783f8-1a07-4995-9f02-7c20d35a9743" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: SecurityClassificationAssignment Core dependency (selects): SecurityClassificationAssignment:   - AssumptionAssignmentSelect --"I assume JoeBloggs can do this activity becuase it has a secutiry classification of "public domain" (assumption on a personOrgAssign with the context of the SecClassAssign) </body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586181792764_27577_83240" xmi:uuid="2d6ca8ab-9f2e-4011-9cb9-f874a66c07bf" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576079349378_693916_53343"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: InterfaceConnectionType Core Dependency (selects): InterfaceDefinitionConnection: - AssumptionAssignmentSelect -- assume it will not overheat because it is designed to be connected to a heat sink (assumption on the component in the context of the connection) - BreakdownElementRealizationSelect -- ??? this functional BE (provide delivery of sufficient fuel to engines) is realized by the definition of the fuel pipe (which has a min curvature property) that connects the tank to the engine - ContractAssignmentSelect -- supplier agrees to share the definition of the connection (optical fibre speed limits) with OEM - InterfaceDefinitionForSelect -- my connection is designed to meet this standard </body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1563885382824_210087_44576" xmi:uuid="37e18708-bd83-4ddc-a7c9-bd82a5ef3e9d" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839358502_906923_14098"/>
      <body>ISO/TC 184/SC 4 WG12 N10988 - ISO/TS 10303-4443 Edition 1: Domain model: For modelling and simulation information in a collaborative system engineering context (MoSSEC) – XMI</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586176839703_694791_77604" xmi:uuid="50e6f599-861f-4d7a-8483-9baa17b20cac" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585584243911_73256_81801"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585818889525_630345_75839"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1582098039105_278557_67598"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1582114955599_165390_73664"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: Architecture, CMT, AMN - CollectionView Core dependency (selects): CollectionView: - InformationUsageRightAssignmentSelect -- reviewed - needed (on PartView) e.g. This CollaborativeModelTemplate (collection of models) had a copyright.</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585229801667_648962_73326" xmi:uuid="5e70145f-c357-41db-9629-d2554ead2d61" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1584348718554_122092_65211"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509956122732_731185_34169"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509966528642_762816_48833"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509969492676_381062_54041"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: MethodResourceAssignment (RequriedResourceAssignment) Core dependency (selects): RequiredResourceAssignment:   - AssumptionAssignmentSelect --- "I assume that a resource is required for an Activity becuase it was required for this similar activity" (assumption on RequiredResourceAssignment in the context of another RequiredResourceAssignment)</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586181323061_551042_82777" xmi:uuid="63e14075-2db0-4dd1-9c19-7ef39983e55f" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1508430785092_767332_50690"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508483096929_238521_31921"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508491001923_668700_40256"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509693202815_831440_31680"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576080350638_418011_54353"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576082207170_356035_56762"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: InterfacePortInstance Core dependency (selects): InterfaceConnectorOccurrence: - AssumptionAssignmentSelect (not OK) -- the fuel pump is assumed to be OK this location because it was used in that location (assumption on one intConnectionOcc because of another intConnectionOcc) - AssumedItemSelect (not OK) -- the fuel pump is assumed to have sufficient capacity in this location - ContractAssignmentSelect (not OK) -- OEM agrees to share the usage of the connect with the supplier of the connector</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586186618502_764562_91529" xmi:uuid="663ac945-a616-41d1-929b-e23494ab5664" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508257735161_474311_51654"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: Verification Core Dependency (selects): Verification - AssumptionAssignmentSelect (not OK) --- "because this verification has taken place, we can assume xyz" e.g. assume certification approval will be granted because the concession has been verified (assumption on the approval, with the context of the verification)</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586183950805_2208_85218" xmi:uuid="7fa600c4-acb3-4a6c-a411-a811bb362348" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585650076523_177820_76808"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508481199714_239099_29975"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508490679786_306244_39225"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508490756531_846999_39353"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508835483031_298173_30876"/>
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509694707203_15058_34522"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: ComponentAssemblyUsage - NextAssembleViewUsage Core dependency (selects): NextAssemblyViewUsage: (AssemblyComponentRelationship) - AssumptionAssignmentSelect (not OK) -- example TBD</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586172440639_897680_73765" xmi:uuid="8551bad4-508e-4451-aa8d-100eb4b0094e" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509527911695_917748_38014"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: BreakdownElementRealization - JustifiedItem Core dependency (selects): BreakdownElementRealization: - JustificationAssignmentSelect Example: "this does-it-malfunction-due-to-max-temperature thermal model results is applicable to this breakdown element because the element it is in a less harsh environment than the element for which it was originally created. " </body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585231173790_672747_74106" xmi:uuid="99268026-99b8-4032-87c7-38662019c3e0" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1552411104473_313272_39440"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: ApplicableMethod - AssumptionContextItem Core dependency (selects): ActivityMethod: - AssumedAssignmentSelect (not in ARM) Example: TBD</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586185760702_185367_88561" xmi:uuid="9b86e494-6a2d-4236-9638-94842238b929" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509981375061_549988_58331"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: SecurityClassification: Core dependency (selects): SecurityClassification:   - AssumptionAssignmentSelect --"Because there is a "top secret" classigicaftion, I assume I can do this" - this is not useful...</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585215534679_716804_67860" xmi:uuid="9f5bb8ba-b705-46ed-aa6e-47305c42cc4a" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509628502041_906909_44450"/>
      <body>4443ed2 proposal: ResourceUsed: Core dependency (selects): RequiredResource:   - AssumptionAssignmentSelect --example: "Assume that five will be sufficient (as that was how many were actually used in another task)."</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585564439634_33320_72098" xmi:uuid="d9aa8e4c-9cd8-455d-89cd-fc269af4320e" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
      <body>Core dependency (RD): function mustBeSubClassOf and mustBeNamedIndividualOf</body>
    </ownedComment>
    <name>Domain_model</name>
    <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_925897_14042" xmi:uuid="13fd71ef-000c-461f-9e60-20b379430645" xmi:type="uml:Package">
      <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512579116654_612974_33869" xmi:uuid="a6f0945d-6adb-4637-9b27-e5dedddfd870" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
        <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_925897_14042"/>
        <body>This module represents information for Organizations and Person(s) in those organizations for use in a collaborative context. This is used by all the other modules. The Figure below provides an overview of this capability. &lt;figuresysml&gt;&lt;id&gt;_18_4_1_13110319_1505983489798_294719_30690&lt;/id&gt;Overview of the Person and Organization capability&lt;/figuresysml&gt;</body>
      </ownedComment>
      <name>PersonOrganization</name>
      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733524_101078_14140" xmi:uuid="116305d7-0732-4142-b402-0a1d46e8abb4" xmi:type="uml:Association">
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733906_969482_15022" xmi:uuid="b2492249-3039-44ef-b9b0-3310ddf56d72" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733524_101078_14140"/>
          <body>This is the relationship that says which organisation a person is in at the moment. If we need to track the history of this person then this shall be an object.&#13; &#13; Also if we need to know how long a person has been in a particular organisation then also has to be an object. This information should be recorded in the Business Data Model, but does not need to appear in the Object Model</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <memberEnd xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733906_411393_15021"/>
        <memberEnd xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733906_696356_15015"/>
        <ownedEnd xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733906_411393_15021" xmi:uuid="934558ae-67ea-4cfd-917e-49eea6cb8c48" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <visibility>public</visibility>
          <type xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733514_450704_14138"/>
          <lowerValue xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734606_175648_17070" xmi:uuid="c1c8d66e-b1ed-4dca-8396-8072c4fb3cf7" xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger"/>
          <upperValue xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734606_931287_17069" xmi:uuid="a7dd16fc-919c-49ff-9172-e8256991fdb0" xmi:type="uml:LiteralUnlimitedNatural">
            <value>*</value>
          </upperValue>
          <association xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733524_101078_14140"/>
