        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733906_676037_14987" xmi:uuid="89037acf-3d25-4714-8395-c652f435e292" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1513010969775_788031_36358" xmi:uuid="2ca59fde-5a5b-4826-b3c7-bc23888e00d0" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733906_676037_14987"/>
            <body>the Organization(s) to which the Organization belongs. The value of this attribute need not be specified. &lt;example&gt;A maintenance team may be part of a manufacturing team that is part of a company&lt;/example&gt;</body>
          </ownedComment>
