    <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_404953_14051" xmi:uuid="14ee21a5-eeab-4170-b31e-b049a9057bed" xmi:type="uml:Package">
      <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512580962701_440716_33892" xmi:uuid="ce76897e-beef-458f-91ec-9df4f326a1f5" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
        <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_404953_14051"/>
        <body>The capability for representing information supporting the capture of decisions in a collaborative context using objects for Assumption, Justification, and Approval. This supports the other capabilities. The Figure below provides an overview of the capability. &lt;figuresysml&gt;&lt;id&gt;_18_4_1_1b310459_1578986503936_108209_54983&lt;/id&gt;Overview of Approval, Justification and Assumption capability&lt;/figuresysml&gt; </body>
      </ownedComment>
      <name>ApprovalAssumptionJustification</name>
      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733786_501358_14570" xmi:uuid="054b68d7-7e8e-4637-8f99-33ec6a6fb8d9" xmi:type="uml:Association">
        <memberEnd xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734056_974504_15763"/>
        <memberEnd xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734046_303912_15727"/>
        <ownedEnd xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734056_974504_15763" xmi:uuid="90809d52-30ae-454f-9d2c-b3d7e2af93bd" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <visibility>public</visibility>
          <type xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733786_640623_14560"/>
          <association xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733786_501358_14570"/>
        </ownedEnd>
      </packagedElement>
      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733786_868603_14562" xmi:uuid="0f2611a2-c231-462a-adc9-738d44391ff7" xmi:type="uml:Class">
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734056_361003_15744" xmi:uuid="5f8a0a20-7731-4dde-8d3e-50e3dd5efdb9" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733786_868603_14562"/>
          <body>A Justification is the identification and description of the reason for something. A Justification references the item or items that are being justified, and any item or items that support that Justification. &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;A Justification is a type of ProgrammeObject therefore, it that it may also have approvals in its own right. An approval may also be the support item, along with any other ProgrammeObject.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;A Justification may justify another Justification, an Assumption or an Approvals, or have another Justification, Assumption or Approval as the support for the Justification.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;There may be JustificationRelationships between Justifications and these may be classified to indicate supporting, contradicting or tracing relationships.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;A Justification for a Study to use a Method for virtual testing may have a SupportItem as a Verification (with Status of "quantitative proof") for a Method satisfying a Requirement.&lt;/example&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>Justification</name>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733886_196479_14861" xmi:uuid="45bf88e0-f9e2-4a1a-ba6b-fe9fac5f808b" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
          <general xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733484_59641_14064"/>
        </generalization>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733966_408865_15352" xmi:uuid="ed37fb01-0472-4d49-9a6a-e11796e4fdd0" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
          <general xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733786_981753_14561"/>
        </generalization>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734056_693832_15745" xmi:uuid="90872907-5b80-47c6-862e-84c556b0ec15" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512562887144_792348_33507" xmi:uuid="087f566d-00a7-4d26-950b-7e646ea7f119" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734056_693832_15745"/>
            <body>the references to the item or items for which the Justification is provided. </body>
          </ownedComment>
          <name>Justifies</name>
          <visibility>public</visibility>
          <type xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733876_637735_14799"/>
          <upperValue xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734646_959186_17562" xmi:uuid="310902f7-edf5-4287-8cec-e817eccd904b" xmi:type="uml:LiteralUnlimitedNatural">
            <value>*</value>
