          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512563005165_891842_33510" xmi:uuid="69f2eac9-528a-40d5-8c0b-8de1fbaa1511" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734046_176714_15728"/>
            <body>the references to Person or Organization who are planned, or were planned, to approve or reject the Approval. The value of this attribute need not be specified. &lt;note&gt;If more than one, then they all have the same status. If different status are needed for each approver then an individual Approval should be used for each approver.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <name>PlannedApprover</name>
          <visibility>public</visibility>
          <type xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733514_450704_14138"/>
