          <body>An Assumption is something that is accepted as true or certain without proof within a context that need not be specified. &lt;note&gt;An Assumption is a type of ProgrammeObject therefore, it there may be a Justification for an Assumption, or an Assumption may be the SupportItem for a Justification&lt;/note&gt;. </body>
