      </ownedComment>
      <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1587973451177_235270_66055" xmi:uuid="833ffed5-4591-4d2b-962c-5713f02646b7" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
        <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733886_429155_14907"/>
        <body>subClassOf 'data format' (subClassOf 'format property' subClassOf 'file') Sub classes: DXF, IGES, ISO 10303-203, ISO 10303-214, ISO 10303-239, ISO 10303-242, TIFF CCITT GR4, VDAFS, VOXEL.</body>
      </ownedComment>
      <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512581344371_715675_33894" xmi:uuid="c3fcc95a-0458-4ad7-953a-52e9e5997c91" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
        <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_811301_14041"/>
        <body>The capability providing the objects used by all other capabilities, defining the common properties used for identification, versions and other management information. It also contains commonly used objects such as properties and documents. &lt;note&gt;Full version management is not included in the collaborative context as it assumed that this will managed by a collaborating Data Management platform. Instead VersionIdentifiers are used to identify the version on the collaborating platform.&lt;/note&gt; The Figure below provides an overview of this capability. &lt;figuresysml&gt;&lt;id&gt;_18_4_1_1b310459_1578989242633_887621_61358&lt;/id&gt;Overview of the Common Resources capability&lt;/figuresysml&gt;</body>
      </ownedComment>
      <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1518166470130_746082_35326" xmi:uuid="c928f134-5800-4c47-a410-20190248eb88" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
        <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733484_663253_14075"/>
        <body>Enhancement: why 1..* for PropertyValue Definition?</body>
      </ownedComment>
