            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733886_429155_14907"/>
            <body>the universal representation for Extension used to identify the type of the DigitalFile. The value is restricted by reference data. The value of this attribute need not be specified.</body>
          </ownedComment>
