            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733886_241163_14908"/>
            <body>the uniform resource identifier for the DigitalFile. The value of this attribute need not be specified. &lt;note&gt;It need not be specified because the content of the file may be stored rather than referenced.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
