            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733996_980238_15496"/>
            <body>the string representing the purpose of the BreakdownElement where the value is restricted reference data. &lt;note&gt;The property can be used to apply business rules to control the BreakdownElement types that can be added to a type of Breakdown, or to control to what other BreakdownElement types they may be connected.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;Physical, Logical.&lt;/example&gt; </body>
