          <body>&lt;note&gt;These designated data types may realize a BreakdownElement. This excludes: &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Breakdowns, BreakdownElementAssociations;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;ActualActivity;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Documents, DigitalFile;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;RequirementShouldBeSatisfied, Verification;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Person, Organization;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;PropertyDefinition, PropertyValue;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Approval;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;All SecurityTrust (Contract, SecurityClassification &amp; InformationRight);&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;all relationship objects that are just types of ManagedObject.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/note&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
