        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734006_889743_15514" xmi:uuid="fb0cd0ed-29c2-456a-bd1d-5ee94c8e1fea" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733746_818006_14434"/>
          <body>A BreakdownElementRealizationAssociation is an association between a BreakdownElement and something that realizes that BreakdownElement.&#13; &lt;note&gt;Identification that the association is in the context of an Architecture is represented by ArchitectureElementInclusion.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;a component that is a technical solution.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;example&gt;a model that represents the BreakdownElement as a whole. &lt;/example&gt; &lt;note&gt;It may be the Subject or Context for an Assumption or Justification.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It may have Approvals.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
