      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733656_811061_14224" xmi:uuid="38c7417d-1456-4ad2-ae06-1474ab40a7b7" xmi:type="uml:Class">
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576681200864_943476_65280" xmi:uuid="a3b506b2-4313-4968-b929-965befbd7e50" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508169348185_314887_44606"/>
          <body>model activity method subclass of: core_v1#activity method</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733926_448978_15122" xmi:uuid="d1ddfc4f-b42e-4124-8f9b-adec0ad771ac" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733656_811061_14224"/>
          <body>A Method defines how to generate the model data for a ModelInstance. &lt;note&gt;It is a type of VersionableObject therefore, it shall have at least one VersionIdentifiers property.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of MethodologyObject therefore, it may reference a detailed definition using FormalDocumentation or InFormalDocumentation Documents.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;FormalDocumentation can be step-by-step instruction sheets, InFormalDocumentation can be a best practise guide.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;note&gt;The resources for a method are represented by MethodResourceAssignment.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;The inputs for a method are represented by MethodInputAssignment.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;A specific usage (output) for a method is represented by ApplicableMethod.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Methods may be identified during formal planning as part of a PlannedActivity and ActualActivity, or during informal planning by PlannedMethod.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;RequirementShouldBeSatisfied is used to indicate that it should satisfy a Requirement.&lt;/note&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>Method</name>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1586182411994_161549_83626" xmi:uuid="17fdde6f-edcf-4b0c-b5c5-7c2b331bce2a" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
          <general xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733876_870517_14803"/>
