      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733666_653781_14228" xmi:uuid="baceb638-1bb2-48d9-803d-832e1184a501" xmi:type="uml:Class">
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733926_703345_15172" xmi:uuid="438bda68-a15e-4616-8761-2aba2b99ec6b" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733666_653781_14228"/>
          <body>An AccessibleModelTypeConstituent represents the definition of something inside the ModelType (a constituent) that is made accessible for use in a CollaborativeModelTemplate. &#13; &lt;example&gt;The naming convention of a surface publication in a CAD model; the numbering convention for a node in a finite element model; a named cell in a spreadsheet.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of VersionableObject therefore, it shall have at least one VersionIdentifiers property.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject. The Identifiers or Names are used to identify the constituent.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Identification that a ModelType is be derived from the constituent is represented by ModelTypeIsDerivedFrom.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Identification that a KeyValueType is be extracted from the constituent is represented by KeyValueTypeIsExtractedFrom.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It may be referenced as a realization of an InterfaceConnectionType or InterfacePortType.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Identification that it is an input to a Method is represented by MethodInputAssignment.&lt;/note&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576510433866_418635_72071" xmi:uuid="93d4970e-cd48-49e8-ae4f-e997b636fd9f" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508136663496_594173_30187"/>
          <body>UUID from AccessibleModelTypeConstituent accessible constituent part core_rd_v1# general part</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>AccessibleModelTypeConstituent</name>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733926_743022_15147" xmi:uuid="3cee52d0-c881-4909-b519-bc39d3db15aa" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
