        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576513532156_109972_73634" xmi:uuid="6326f3ce-37b3-4582-b6a3-9335500d5dea" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1552417346959_525971_42076"/>
          <body>UUID from ApplicableMethod.methodRelationship applicable method relationship sub class of core_v1#activity method relationship</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734886_326277_18308" xmi:uuid="cdd8835e-30e3-43bf-a5b8-a2e858ec939b" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734406_995789_16448"/>
          <body>An ApplicableMethod is the definition of Methods applicable for generating specific ModelTypes independent of the CollaborativeModelTemplate. &lt;note&gt;If a method can be used to generate multiple ModelType and has different input types for the different usages, then inputs may be represented by MethodInputAssignment.&#13;&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of ObjectWithPropertyValues therefore, it may have PropertyValues.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576512964444_933584_72882" xmi:uuid="f19334aa-1281-4858-9365-ba1aea401df2" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1548944466853_151831_71788"/>
          <body>UUID from ApplicableMethod model applicable activity method subclass of: core_v1#activity method</body>
        </ownedComment>
