          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1508162637451_649032_38102"/>
          <body>extracted from part version relationship sub class of: core_rd_v1#derivation part version relationship</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733926_63982_15090" xmi:uuid="d36ba870-c508-4f56-a2f7-f11c159ed1e4" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733656_171926_14220"/>
          <body>A KeyValueTypeIsExtractedFrom is a relationship between a KeyValueType and the item that it may be ExtractedFrom in the Context of a CollaborativeModelTemplate. &lt;note&gt;To have the same relationship in more than one template without duplication, the CollaborativeModelTemplate IsComposedOf reference property may be used to combine templates.&lt;/note&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>KeyValueTypeIsExtractedFrom</name>
        <ownedRule xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1551107893870_66739_44392" xmi:uuid="4db38c98-322f-4c53-88c4-60d99914c0aa" xmi:type="uml:Constraint">
