    <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_956410_14047" xmi:uuid="519656a5-8fd4-4459-a470-47929606fd49" xmi:type="uml:Package">
      <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512638017622_30289_32527" xmi:uuid="fd86afd5-26e2-4cfd-887e-30fa596d72d0" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
        <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733474_956410_14047"/>
        <body>The CollaborativeProcessManagement capability represents information concerning the management of activities in a collaborative context. It is used to identify what was planned compared to what actually happened; what resources should have been used compared to what were actually used. The Figure below provides an overview of this capability. &lt;figuresysml&gt;&lt;id&gt;_18_4_1_1b310459_1578988562135_774237_60276&lt;/id&gt;Overview of the Collaborative Process Management capability&lt;/figuresysml&gt;</body>
      </ownedComment>
      <name>CollaborativeProcessManagement</name>
      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734446_749563_16543" xmi:uuid="0da16b73-c5fc-44ee-a263-3635ba32bbac" xmi:type="uml:Association">
