          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733716_425901_14382"/>
          <body>A ResourceUsed represents the resources that are expected to be used as part of a PlannedActivity or were used as part of aActualActivity. It may have properties. &lt;example&gt;Properties may be used to declare how many of a resource were used.&lt;/example&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
