          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509626831653_398018_42882"/>
          <body>actual modelling activity subclassof corev1#actual activity</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733986_264467_15441" xmi:uuid="6bca9c42-8bee-4fd1-afc9-69c1260967cb" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733716_95163_14381"/>
          <body>An ActualActivity is the activity on a Subject that actually happened, or is happening.&#13; It may reference Methods and other resources that were used. &lt;example&gt;Examples of Subjects are: a ModelInstance where the results are being generated; an AssociativeModelNetwork where the a number of ModelInstances are being sequenced; a Method or CollaborativeModelTemplate that is being developed.&lt;/example&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1584357963977_429078_73206" xmi:uuid="dda3b664-23b7-4333-9098-0109981c85e6" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
