        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733916_936964_15047" xmi:uuid="3edaaa1b-16b0-4110-902d-258f2c913af3" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512667871355_797365_32946" xmi:uuid="432d102d-9fa2-46f3-9337-1b9138ef3ab1" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733916_936964_15047"/>
            <body>the string for the state where the value is restricted by reference data. This has a value to indicate that the verification has not yet been done, and values for pass and fail with varying levels of assurance.</body>
