        </ownedEnd>
      </packagedElement>
      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579426655_151161_79248" xmi:uuid="3b690809-04ea-4032-852d-fcff9dec71c2" xmi:type="uml:Class">
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585583100899_533587_81025" xmi:uuid="1cc23e77-6306-4258-a84d-07cab6c2405b" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1583761348887_205050_71286"/>
          <body>architecture UUID from Architecture subclass of core_v1#collection</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579453008_870023_79291" xmi:uuid="adab5d68-cdae-446e-b8e7-9c55bf4dca04" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579426655_151161_79248"/>
          <body>An Architecture is the container for the set of elements that define the design and structure of a system of interest. &lt;note&gt;It is a type of VersionableObject therefore, it shall have at least one VersionIdentifiers property.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;References to items included in the Architecture are represented by ArchitectureElementInclusion.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Assumptions and Justifications may be applied to Architectures, their elements (represented by ArchitectureElementInclusion) and realizations (represented by ArchitectureRealizationAssociation).&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;A Breakdown may be a BreakdownOf an Architecture therefore, an Architecture may contain other Architectures.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Architectures may have Properties (with no traceability) or be the ValueOf a ValueInstanceObject (with traceability).&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;RequirementShouldBeSatisfied is used to indicate that it should satisfy a Requirement.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Architectures may be Inputs to a Study therefore, the architecture may be used as a reference in the study, updated during the study, or be the context for something in the study.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;A Study Creates an Architecture. Therefore a Study may be the source of the architecture, or the architecture may be the output of the study.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585583699125_228731_81599" xmi:uuid="b483047b-af9c-4776-84cd-c3a534d4424b" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1583761803957_244470_71311"/>
          <body>architecture evolved from relationship UUID from Architecture.IsEvolvedFrom subclass of core_v1# collection version sequence relationship</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585584729194_701933_82039" xmi:uuid="bcd8f91a-df2e-4add-a4d2-5ea613f3ccce" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1583763090903_455_72055"/>
          <body>architecture of UUID from Architecture.ArchitectureOf subclassof core_v1#collection assignment</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>Architecture</name>
        <ownedRule xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585585964589_117080_84094" xmi:uuid="a7f4f98b-2442-44c4-9abd-3e21c3ad6837" xmi:type="uml:Constraint">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585585964589_550219_84096" xmi:uuid="947fca6b-dac4-42da-ba6c-45d417988d5a" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585585964589_117080_84094"/>
            <body>an Architecture shall not include a Breakdown that references the same Architecture as an ArchitectureOf, also included Breakdowns shall not have a BreakdownElement that references the Architecture as an ArchitectureOf.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <name>NotCircular</name>
          <constrainedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579844430_464518_79368"/>
          <specification xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585585964589_36321_84095" xmi:uuid="602f325c-4c18-4bce-89a6-e7917a813d32" xmi:type="uml:OpaqueExpression">
            <body>The architecture shall not include a Breakdown that has a BreakdownElement that the architecture is an ArchitectureOf and it shall not include elements that have itself as the BreakdownOf item.</body>
            <language>English</language>
          </specification>
        </ownedRule>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579588605_814165_79356" xmi:uuid="1ac7fd5d-aa96-4481-9124-8abca20d3e49" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
          <general xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733876_908706_14804"/>
