        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579844430_464518_79368" xmi:uuid="cd497dc2-3018-481e-ad38-36f714359166" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579873186_417358_79395" xmi:uuid="dbd26161-0399-4849-bb68-fb3e0e62b770" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579844430_464518_79368"/>
            <body>the system of interest that is the subject of the Architecture. &lt;note&gt;Circularities should be avoided therefore, the architecture should not include elements that reference itself as the ArchitectureOf or the BreakdownOf either directly or via their own elements.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;This enables architectures to include other architecture where an architecture may be an ArchitectureOf a BreakdownElement that is an element of a Breakdown that is included in another Architecture.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <name>ArchitectureOf</name>
          <visibility>public</visibility>
          <type xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733886_174422_14819"/>
          <association xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1585579844430_998580_79367"/>
