          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733806_578798_14622"/>
          <body>DistributionObject is the abstract object from which entities inherit distribution properties. &lt;note&gt;It is a type of ManagedObject therefore, it may have a ClassifiedAs string to define the type of distribution.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject.&lt;/note&gt;&#13; </body>
