          <body>Class: non-parametric distribution part Sub Class of: realized individual part</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576489836353_552024_62799" xmi:uuid="9f1e6071-2523-4ad5-adfa-5089c0ea4f82" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1509695819679_616050_35868"/>
          <body>distribution data document assignment sub class of: description document assignment</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734066_238176_15785" xmi:uuid="b7c3e9a0-4a92-46da-ac81-ef9b2383843b" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733806_235011_14623"/>
          <body>A NonParametricDistribution is a distribution that may be defined using DistributionData Documents rather than defined using parameters. &lt;note&gt;A distribution defined using parameters is a ParametricDistribution.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of ManagedObject therefore, it may have a ClassifiedAs string to define the type of distribution.&lt;/note&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>NonParametricDistribution</name>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734066_285845_15780" xmi:uuid="a0127e1f-59f2-4edb-9e56-fb3c02520139" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
