            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734026_393683_15622"/>
            <body>one of the pair of InterfacePortType for the relationship. If the type of relationship implies a hierarchy or flow this is the "child" or "to" object.</body>
          </ownedComment>
