        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734026_852930_15623" xmi:uuid="a3a5a397-0b50-4d13-afaf-db17befbda60" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1512999555497_959486_32976" xmi:uuid="900c5a52-83f9-4df5-84be-cee65f5dcdc8" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734026_852930_15623"/>
            <body>the string to indicate how the ports are related. It is restricted by reference data. &lt;note&gt;This may be used as an indication of how the connected InterfacePortType or their realizations may be delegated or collated.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
