          <body>An InterfaceSpecification provides a definition of the necessary attributes for one or more items that are part of an interface.&#13; It may inherit from other InterfaceSpecification. &lt;example&gt;A Simple Bolted Flange, a Glued Flange, a non-linear Bolted Flange.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;example&gt;One Way Thermal Coupling, two way thermal coupling.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;example&gt;USB interface specification inherits from a USB spatial, a USB data and a USB power interface specification.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;example&gt;A bolt pattern interface specification with a pitch and angle definition for the pattern inherits definition for minimum bolt distance from an edge or radius.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of VersionableObject therefore, it shall have at least one VersionIdentifiers property.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of IdentifiableObject therefore, it shall have Identifiers and may have a Descriptions, Names, other management information from ManagedObject.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of MethodologyObject therefore, it may define the specification using Documents.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;A table of standard sizes.&lt;/example&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of ObjectWithPropertyDefinitions therefore, it may have PropertyDefinitions.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;It is a type of ObjectWithPropertyValues therefore, it may have Properties where there are set values for a PropertyDefinition.&lt;/note&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1588004757112_503612_69049" xmi:uuid="f7498e78-103f-4297-9323-c9a4df1c8fb3" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_13110319_1588005266605_296790_69083"/>
          <body>inherits from interface specification relationship SubclassOf hierarchy interface specification relationship SubClassOf interface specification version relationship</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>InterfaceSpecification</name>
        <ownedRule xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1581338066571_334557_69488" xmi:uuid="16fcfa8f-b243-471e-97ef-2a28c179667c" xmi:type="uml:Constraint">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1581338066571_595556_69490" xmi:uuid="7d939605-b520-4e22-9fca-986c15183461" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1581338066571_334557_69488"/>
            <body>when it has an InheritsFrom reference it shall not point to itself.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <name>notInheritSelf</name>
          <constrainedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733746_683739_14437"/>
          <specification xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1581338066571_997335_69489" xmi:uuid="b979ebf3-9c00-46a4-8d4f-953e80ec6c34" xmi:type="uml:OpaqueExpression">
            <body>self.InheritsFrom &lt;&gt; self</body>
            <language>OCL2.0</language>
          </specification>
        </ownedRule>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734936_288580_18401" xmi:uuid="17e9f297-5f6c-4f30-bad0-475f99667e25" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
