            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733946_367951_15215"/>
            <body>the items managed by a study. The value of this attribute need not be specified. &lt;note&gt;This may include:&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;other studies to manage a hierarchy of studies;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;several AssociativeModelNetwork representing the packages of work that is being done for the study;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;several MethodologyObjects that are being developed during the study (with the StudyType equal to "methodology development").&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;An item shall be managed by only one study.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;An AssociativeModelNetwork shall have a ManagedBy reference to a study. It is recommended but not mandated, that the study includes the reciprocal Manages reference to the AssociativeModelNetwork.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
          </ownedComment>
