            <body>the items that are inputs to a study. The value of this attribute need not be specified. &lt;note&gt;This is used to identify previous work that is relevant to, or reused by the Study. It includes other Studies, AssociativeModelNetworks, and Architectures&lt;/note&gt; </body>
