        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734086_514036_15849" xmi:uuid="bf57461c-a64a-44a6-8915-c053fa156e6f" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733826_344400_14684"/>
          <body>A Contract is a binding agreement among the Parties to whom the contract applies. It may point to instances of Document that are the contract. &lt;note&gt;Contracts may be related to other contracts represented by ContractRelationship&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Contracts may have Approvals; be the Subject of Assumptions; or be the Support for a Justification.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;Contracts may have AssignedTo references to the items under contract.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;Contracts may cover for example, the delivery of data as part of a collaborative Study, or the execution of activity objects.&lt;/example&gt; </body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>Contract</name>
