        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733956_567182_15293" xmi:uuid="75d6d99e-576d-430b-932c-9c44455d1fb5" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_13110319_1513008100154_361952_35306" xmi:uuid="6fcf843f-375c-40fc-926c-82cd0c857c24" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733956_567182_15293"/>
            <body>Initially the ModelInstance is used to identify that something needs to be modelled or simulated. Then after completion this property is used to link to the specific detailed numeric data/content - a file or PDM reference/URL(s). The value of this attribute need not be specified.</body>
          </ownedComment>
