          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734616_30514_17252" xmi:uuid="b267489a-1025-4586-8d93-a6d9da5200db" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733956_692811_15298"/>
            <body>the Person or Organization responsible for coordinating the execution of the model instances that make up the AssociativeModelNetwork. </body>
