        <ownedAttribute xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733956_271959_15315" xmi:uuid="505c697c-70e6-4028-a9cc-8715359eca35" xmi:type="uml:Property">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1512660857586_399165_32896" xmi:uuid="432f452d-81fb-4103-8895-58b7e36f2784" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733956_271959_15315"/>
            <body>the reference to the Study that is managing the AssociativeModelNetwork. &lt;note&gt;A Study may have a Manages reference to an AssociativeModelNetwork as the reciprocal to this reference. It is recommended, but not mandatory, that the study includes the reciprocal Manages reference to this reference.&lt;/note&gt;</body>
          </ownedComment>
