            <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839733956_664620_15318"/>
            <body>the Person or Organization responsible for coordinating the execution of the ModelInstances that BelongsTo the AssociativeModelNetwork.</body>
          </ownedComment>
