      <packagedElement xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734386_156473_16419" xmi:uuid="8eebe3ad-896c-40f0-9972-35a7f3529ce1" xmi:type="uml:Class">
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734866_915750_18277" xmi:uuid="7987353f-c67e-4357-afae-3d2f79bc89ee" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734386_156473_16419"/>
          <body>A PlannedMethod is the identification of the Method that is planned to be used to generate the ResultsDocuments for the referenced Output (ModelInstance or QualityReportInstance). &lt;note&gt;The expected usage of this object is during early life-cycle phases before detailed planning is available that uses PlannedActivity.&#13;&lt;/note&gt; &lt;note&gt;There may be many PlannedMethod for a ModelInstance.&lt;/note&gt; &lt;example&gt;Multiple methods can be used for example for results data generation, quality checking reports and visualisation.&lt;/example&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedComment xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1576682159966_619460_66621" xmi:uuid="bef41d3b-5a25-447b-9f87-2a79d02062ea" xmi:type="uml:Comment">
          <annotatedElement xmi:idref="_18_4_1_1b310459_1549278151684_65176_40821"/>
          <body>&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt; &lt;p&gt;UUID from PlannedMethod&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;planned activity method assignment&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;subclass of: core_v1#activity method &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <name>PlannedMethod</name>
        <generalization xmi:id="_18_4_1_1b310459_1505839734866_775415_18276" xmi:uuid="846576b6-9a55-4d3b-9384-86e1fc7b4fe5" xmi:type="uml:Generalization">
